name: Localist-events-list
tagline: PHP implementation of Localist API to display event list on our site
body:
### Welcome
To use this code, you'll need to be a Localist client. This utilizes their API to display a list of events on a public site.

### Authors and Contributors
Created in 2013 by @umhbwebservices

### Support or Contact
Having trouble? Feel free to email us at webservices@umhb.edu. We'll do what we can, when we can.
